@735 = ~Chameleon~
@736 = ~Chameleon (Illusion)
Level: 3
Range: 0
Duration: 3 rounds + 1 round/level
Casting Time: 4
Area of Effect: caster
Saving Throw: none

Looking for invisibility, the warlord reached a softened but still useful result, this spell.
Chameleon makes the warlord almost invisible. In fact, he is not really invisible but blends into the background by becoming transparent. He then gains a bonus in hiding of +1 to AC and +1 to saving throws.
As long as he moves he can be spotted. But if stops moving and stands still for 1 round, then he will really become invisible. He loses this advantage if he casts a spell or takes an offensive action, but any new round standing still would make him invisible again. He can repeat it as many times as desired as the spell lasts.~
