Area of Effect: caster
Saving Throw: none

This spell allows the warlord to better resist to fire and cold. When he casts the spell, he must choose against which element he wishes being protected, then he gains 4% per level (max 80%) of resistance against that element, be it of magical origin or not: spells, weapons, wands, breathes, etc.
